gw.api.contact

Interface AdditionalInterestContainer

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    BOPBuilding, BusinessVehicle, ContractorsEquipment, CPBuilding, HOPDwelling, PersonalVehicle

    public interface AdditionalInterestContainer
    Delegate interface for entities that contain additional interests. This interface is used primarily in the UI for displaying and editing the Additional Interests on an entity that contains Additional Interests (i.e. a PAVehicle or a BOPBuilding)

      • removeFromAdditionalInterestDetails

        void removeFromAdditionalInterestDetails(AddlInterestDetail interestDetail)
        Removes the given AddlInterestDetail from this container. If this detail is the last one on the PolicyAddlInterest, the PolicyAddlInterest is removed as well. If the AccountContactRole (an AdditionalInterest) is new, that is removed as well, and finally if the AccountContact itself is new and no longer in use, the Account Contact is removed as well.
        Parameters:
        interestDetail - the AddlInterestDetail to remove from the container

      • addAdditionalInterestDetail

        AddlInterestDetail addAdditionalInterestDetail(PolicyAddlInterest policyAdditionalInterest)
        Add a new AdditionalInterestDetail to this container and the given PolicyAddlInterest
        Parameters:
        policyAdditionalInterest - the PolicyAddlInterest to connect the new AdditionalinterestDetail to
        Returns:
        the newly created AdditionalInterestDetail

      • addAdditionalInterestDetail

        AddlInterestDetail addAdditionalInterestDetail(Contact contact)
        Add a new AdditionalInterestDetail to this container linked to the given Contact. If that Contact does not have an AccountContact for the proper Account, that is created. If the AccountContact does not have an AdditionalInterest role, that is created; and finally if the Policy does not have a PolicyAddlInterest role, that role is created.
        Parameters:
        contact - the Contact to create an AddlInterestDetail for
        Returns:
        the newly created AddlInterestDetail

      • createAndAddAdditionalInterestDetail

        AddlInterestDetail createAndAddAdditionalInterestDetail(ContactType contactType)
        Create a new AddlInterestDetail for a new Contact of the given ContactType. Creates the AccountContact, AccountContactRole and PolicyAddlInterest as well.
        Parameters:
        contactType - the type of the new Contact to create and link the AddlInterestDetail to
        Returns:
        the newly created AddlInterestDetail

      • getAdditionalInterestDetailsForPolicyAddlInterest

        AddlInterestDetail[] getAdditionalInterestDetailsForPolicyAddlInterest(PolicyAddlInterest policyAdditionalInterest)
        Get all the AddlInterestDetails on this container for the given PolicyAddlInterest role
        Parameters:
        policyAdditionalInterest - the PolicyAddlInterest to look for common AddlInterestDetails on
        Returns:
        all AddlInterestDetails linked to this container and the given PolicyAddlInterest
